Douglas McPhail https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Douglas_McPhail 0 Douglas McPhail (April 16, 1914 – December 6, 1944) was an American actor and singer, active from the 1930s to 1944, when he committed suicide. He was married to Betty Jaynes. Douglas_McPhail ( April_16_,_1914 – December_6_,_1944 ) was an_American_actor_and_singer , active from the_1930s_to_1944 , when he committed suicide .
